AllClaimed(address,uint256).details: Emitted when coins and bonusses are claimed in `claim`.

params.amount: Amount of coins that were claimed.
params.beneficiary: Address that received the coins and bonuses.

Vested(address,uint256,uint256,uint256,u.details: Emitted when a vesting schedule is created in `addClaim`.

params.amount: Amount of coins to be vested.
params.beneficiary: Address that receives the coins and bonuses.
params.bonusAmount: The bonus that becomes available during the vesting period.
params.duration: Duration in seconds of the vesting period.

addClaim(address,uint256,uint256,uint256.details: Accessible only by owner. Emits the `Vested` event.

params.amount: Amount of coins to be vested.
params.beneficiary: Address that receives the coins and bonuses.
params.bonusAmount: The bonus that becomes available during the vesting period.
params.duration: Duration in seconds of the vesting period.

claimAll(address).details: Accessible only by owner. Can be called many times. Reverts if nothing can be claimed. Transfers the claimable coins and bonuses to `account`. Emits the `AllClaimed` event.

params.account: Address that receives the coins and bonuses.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

paused().details: Returns true if the contract is paused, and false otherwise.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

rescue().details: Accessible only by immutable `rescuer` defined at construction.

returns._0: Current statics about the vesting schedules of a beneficiary.
Statics about the vesting schedules of a beneficiary at a certain point in time. This allows to project the future state of the vesting schedules.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

MIN_FUTURE_END.details: Minimum days in the future that the vesting must end.

allBonuses.details: Total amount of bonuses that have or will become available (claimed or not) over all vestings.

allTokensClaimed.details: Total amount of tokens that have been claimed over all vestings.

allTokensVested.details: Total amount of tokens that are vested over all vestings.

token.details: The token must implement the ERC20 interface.

addClaim(address,uint256,uint256,uint256.notice: Creates a new vesting schedule for a beneficiary.

claimAll(address).notice: Claims (transfers) all currently free coins and claimable bonuses for a beneficiary.

pause().notice: Pauses the contract. `addClaim` and `claimAll` cannot be called.

rescue().notice: Rescues entire `token` balance from the contract.

token().notice: The token that is being vested.

userdoc.notice: A token holder contract that releases its token balance according to a vesting schedule.
